    {
        "id": "comment_node",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "cv_flow",
        "name": "CV Template - Dynamic Data Flow",
        "info": "This flow creates a professional CV template that accepts dynamic data.\n\nTo use:\n1. Inject CV data in JSON format\n2. The data will be displayed in a professional CV layout\n3. Use the 'Reload CV' button to refresh the display\n\nData Structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"title\": \"Job Title\",\n  \"email\": \"email@example.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"+00-000-0000\",\n  \"address\": \"Full Address\",\n  \"skills\": [\"Skill1\", \"Skill2\"],\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"company\": \"Company Name\",\n      \"position\": \"Position\",\n      \"startDate\": \"Month Year\",\n      \"endDate\": \"Month Year\",\n      \"tasks\": [\"Task 1\", \"Task 2\"]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"schools\": [\n    {\n      \"degree\": \"Degree Name\",\n      \"schoolName\": \"School Name\",\n      \"startDate\": \"Month Year\",\n      \"endDate\": \"Month Year\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"links\": {\n    \"github\": \"url\",\n    \"orcid\": \"url\",\n    \"ieee\": \"url\"\n  },\n  \"imageSrc\": \"image_url\"\n}\n```",
        "x": 170,
        "y": 40,
        "wires": []
    }
